er second Olympics after drawing a blank in the previous edition.\", \"from\": 506, \"to\": 910, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 543, \"end\": 548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999702003878, \"rank\": 2.979962616579612e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 609, \"end\": 616, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jhajjar_district\", \"score\": 0.6444398318426116, \"rank\": 0.4328295935361357, \"text\": \"Jhajjar\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jhajjar_district\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jhajjar_district\"}, {\"begin\": 620, \"end\": 627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"score\": 0.9999999999727152, \"rank\": 1.707317938721082e-11, \"text\": \"Haryana\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\"}, {\"begin\": 694, \"end\": 697, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"score\": 0.999987548125764, \"rank\": 1.0868450974313147e-05, \"text\": \"Kim\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\"}, {\"begin\": 698, \"end\": 702, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Itzy\", \"score\": 0.9999999956855845, \"rank\": 4.314344287663745e-09, \"text\": \"Yeji\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Itzy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Itzy\"}, {\"begin\": 765, \"end\": 771, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jin_Ye\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jin Ye\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jin_Ye\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/reso